	<h1 class="title">你们科技大佬那么爱谈时尚，就不能先穿得齐整点儿？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Vanessa Friedman</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-10-17 12:48:30 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2918/medium/2918.jpg?1436654706" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


